The '''École nationale des sciences appliquées d'Al Hoceima''' (National School of Applied Sciences of Al Hoceima) is a [[Morocco|Moroccan]] public [[engineering school]] located in [[Al Hoceima]], [[Al Hoceïma Province]]. It is a part of Morocco's [[Écoles nationales des sciences appliquées|national network of schools of applied sciences]]. 

==Curriculum==
Three programmes are offered at the institution:
*[[Computer engineering]]
*[[Civil engineering]]
*[[Environmental engineering]]

